wdi2-SP.POP.1564.TO.def: Total population between the ages 15 to 64. Population is based on the de facto definition of population, which counts all residents regardless of legal status or citizenship.
wdi2-SP.POP.1564.TO.name: Population ages 15-64
wdi2-SP.POP.1564.TO.source: World Bank staff estimates using the World Bank's total population and age/sex distributions of the United Nations Population Division's World Population Prospects: 2019 Revision.
